---
description: Nekro Agent for Windows project rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow the repository rules in `AGENTS.md`.

Key constraints:
- Python 3.11, PyQt6, Windows-first launcher, WSL runtime backend.
- Default text line endings are CRLF; `*.sh` stays LF.
- Reuse `ui/widgets.py` shared dialogs, wizard base classes, and button factories before adding local UI variants.
- Surface actionable WSL/Docker/Compose/download/update errors with command output where available.
- Validate ports through `core.port_utils.validate_port_bindings`.
- Verify with `uv run poe lint`; it includes Pyright.
